    "content": "<h2>Teplo a jeho šíření</h2>\n<p><strong>Teplo (Q)</strong> je energie, která přechází z teplejšího tělesa na chladnější. Jednotka: <strong>joule (J)</strong>.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 480 110' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <rect x='10' y='10' width='140' height='90' rx='8' fill='#fef2f2' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='80' y='32' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#991b1b' font-size='11'>Vedení</text>\n  <text x='80' y='50' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>pevné látky</text>\n  <line x1='30' y1='70' x2='130' y2='70' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='3'/><circle cx='30' cy='70' r='5' fill='#fecaca' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1'/><circle cx='55' cy='70' r='5' fill='#fecaca' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1'/><circle cx='80' cy='70' r='5' fill='#fecaca' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1'/><circle cx='105' cy='70' r='5' fill='#fecaca' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1'/><circle cx='130' cy='70' r='5' fill='#fecaca' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1'/>\n  <rect x='170' y='10' width='140' height='90' rx='8' fill='#fef3c7' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='240' y='32' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#92400e' font-size='11'>Proudění</text>\n  <text x='240' y='50' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>kapaliny, plyny</text>\n  <path d='M200,85 Q220,60 240,85 Q260,60 280,85' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.5' marker-end='url(#tp)'/><text x='240' y='98' text-anchor='middle' fill='#f59e0b' font-size='9'>↑ teplý stoupá</text>\n  <rect x='330' y='10' width='140' height='90' rx='8' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='400' y='32' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='11'>Záření</text>\n  <text x='400' y='50' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>i vakuem</text>\n  <circle cx='370' cy='75' r='12' fill='#fef3c7' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1'/><line x1='388' y1='75' x2='398' y2='75' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='382.72792206135784' y1='87.72792206135786' x2='389.7989898732233' y2='94.79898987322332' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='370' y1='93' x2='370' y2='103' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='357.27207793864216' y1='87.72792206135786' x2='350.2010101267767' y2='94.79898987322333' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='352' y1='75' x2='342' y2='75' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='357.27207793864216' y1='62.27207793864214' x2='350.2010101267767' y2='55.20101012677667' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='370' y1='57' x2='370' y2='47' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='382.72792206135784' y1='62.27207793864214' x2='389.7989898732233' y2='55.201010126776666' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <defs><marker id='tp' viewBox='0 0 6 6' refX='5' refY='3' markerWidth='4' markerHeight='4' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L6,3 L0,6Z' fill='#f59e0b'/></marker></defs>\n</svg></div><h3>Vzorec</h3>\n<div class='formula'>$$Q = m \\cdot c \\cdot \\Delta t$$</div>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>teplo</td><td>Q</td><td>J</td></tr>\n<tr><td>hmotnost</td><td>m</td><td>kg</td></tr>\n<tr><td>měrná tepelná kapacita</td><td>c</td><td>J/(kg·°C)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>změna teploty</td><td>Δt</td><td>°C</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Měrná tepelná kapacita</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Látka</th><th>c [J/(kg·°C)]</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Voda</td><td>4 180</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Železo</td><td>450</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Měď</td><td>383</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Vzduch</td><td>1 005</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Způsoby šíření tepla</h3>\n<p><strong>Vedení</strong> — v pevných látkách (kov, vaření na sporáku).</p>\n<p><strong>Proudění</strong> — v kapalinách a plynech (ohřev vody, topení).</p>\n<p><strong>Záření</strong> — i vakuem (Slunce → Země).</p>"
  }
}
